# ── Never commit downloaded course material ──────────────────────────────
# This tool downloads copyrighted TUM course files to each user's OWN machine.
# Those files must never be redistributed or committed to this repo.
TUM_Archive/
*.pdf
*.zip
*.pptx
*.docx
*.mp4
downloads/
archive/

# ── Never commit anything that could leak a session ──────────────────────
*cookie*
*cookies*
*session*
*token*
*.sqlite
*.har

# ── Scan / download logs the tool may emit ───────────────────────────────
*_scan_log.json
*_download_failures.json

# ── Internal planning docs (not for the public repo) ─────────────────────
BRIEF.md
WORK_NOTE*.md

# ── OS / editor noise ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/
*.log
node_modules/
